<p><strong>异想世界</strong></p>
<p>玛莉安·派克亚洲首展</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200813/cdf0d313423b46fcaa9b8e0638b2381f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>小红书@River Min </p>
